snippet.title: Meow Moments   Celebrating Together (Trailer)
snippet.description:
Join the feline festivities in special moments! Find cats friends in vibrant celebrations where popping balloons is as relaxing and satisfying as bubble wrap! To get off to a good start, celebrate Copacabana beach in Rio de Janeiro during the New Year.

Developed by Mens Sana Interactive
Ilustrations by Katia Numakura
Music by Tatyana Jacques

Jan/2024 on Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2647300/Meow_Moments_Celebrating_Together/?utm_source=msi_yt&utm_campaign=mwmm_trailer
